## FLEXIBILITY CLAUSE

The creator retains the right to **discount, waive, or restructure** the flat fee and/or royalty for any season or deal at her sole discretion.

This may include (but is not limited to):
- Educational partnerships
- Non-profit collaborations
- Indie productions with global impact potential
- Equity-sharing or joint-ownership models
- Bundled or multi-season agreements

All changes must be formally agreed to in writing.

> ⚠️ Regardless of commercial terms, **creator credit and IP ownership are non-negotiable and fully retained.**

